{"tid":2260811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"難捨奧巴馬卸任　美女孩大哭片段fb瘋傳　奧巴馬親留言安慰","createTime":"2020-10-28T00:56:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T02:03:45.000Z","uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b875db973933254ac04616dd33221a8042eee802","tid":2260811,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T00:56:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20160222/s00005/1456137785690/【短片-網上熱話】難捨奧巴馬卸任-美女孩大哭片段fb瘋傳-奧巴馬親留言安慰\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20160222%2Fs00005%2F1456137785690%2F%E3%80%90%E7%9F%AD%E7%89%87-%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1%E3%80%91%E9%9B%A3%E6%8D%A8%E5%A5%A7%E5%B7%B4%E9%A6%AC%E5%8D%B8%E4%BB%BB-%E7%BE%8E%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%A9%E5%A4%A7%E5%93%AD%E7%89%87%E6%AE%B5fb%E7%98%8B%E5%82%B3-%E5%A5%A7%E5%B7%B4%E9%A6%AC%E8%A6%AA%E7%95%99%E8%A8%80%E5%AE%89%E6%85%B0&d=BCqMRPjRs%2BrlYbPtDS4RDHs01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=c2c394d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20160222%2Fs00005%2F1456137785690%2F%E3%80%90%E7%9F%AD%E7%89%87-%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1%E3%80%91%E9%9B%A3%E6%8D%A8%E5%A5%A7%E5%B7%B4%E9%A6%AC%E5%8D%B8%E4%BB%BB-%E7%BE%8E%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%A9%E5%A4%A7%E5%93%AD%E7%89%87%E6%AE%B5fb%E7%98%8B%E5%82%B3-%E5%A5%A7%E5%B7%B4%E9%A6%AC%E8%A6%AA%E7%95%99%E8%A8%80%E5%AE%89%E6%85%B0&h=65c2f69c\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20160222/s00005/1456137785690/【短片-網上熱話】難捨奧巴馬卸任-美女孩大哭片段fb瘋傳-奧巴馬親留言安慰</a><br />\n<br />\n美國總統選舉進行得如火如荼，意味著現任總統奧巴馬亦卸任在即。美國一名女孩日前因接受不了奧巴馬的離任，在家嚎啕大哭，結果被祖母錄下來，並將片段放上網，更引來奧巴馬親自留言安慰。<br />\n<br />\n片段中祖母哈利斯（Caprina D Harris）日前在facebook上載片段，心痛孫女在家哭得那麼慘。片段中的小女孩哭道：「我沒準備好要有一個新總統。」哈利斯表示孫女自出生起，奧巴馬就已經在任，所以一時間難以接受奧巴馬要卸任的事實。更加巧合的是，小女孩跟奧巴馬是同一天生日。<br />\n<br />\n片段在短短幾天内獲瘋傳數千次，甚至引起奧巴馬的注意，親自在哈利斯的facebook留言，叫她好好安慰小女孩。奧巴馬說：「哈利斯，請叫她不要流淚，因爲我哪裏都不會去。我離開白宮後，我就會跟她一樣是個普通市民。當她長大後，她就可以來找我，在這之前，我會繼續留意她的來信，我們以後還可以一起慶祝生日！」"},{"pid":"b532dbfc9c335aaab8e49b773101a63eb5c2d711","tid":2260811,"uid":1654,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T00:57:54.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">20160222</span></span>"},{"pid":"3a1bf3507dce2b454288f74471891d0bdd384fb7","tid":2260811,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T01:00:35.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">哈利斯表示孫女自出生起，奧巴馬就已經在任，所以一時間難以接受奧巴馬要卸任的事實。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n習大大又要拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4775072beab7f2aa52cadc9dd9ecd70bd4f2371d","tid":2260811,"uid":108347,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T01:02:31.000Z","msg":"Obama pr做得好係事實"},{"pid":"71ab89dfaed83c7889b844e3d0e72b9afe25c536","tid":2260811,"uid":78074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a1bf3507dce2b454288f74471891d0bdd384fb7","tid":2260811,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T01:00:35.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">哈利斯表示孫女自出生起，奧巴馬就已經在任，所以一時間難以接受奧巴馬要卸任的事實。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n習大大又要拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T01:04:46.000Z","msg":"Sorry習大大係終身制，唔會卸任"},{"pid":"769c9a528ac98f531c86c76d5852064e4d1a9859","tid":2260811,"uid":4574,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4775072beab7f2aa52cadc9dd9ecd70bd4f2371d","tid":2260811,"uid":108347,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T01:02:31.000Z","msg":"Obama pr做得好係事實"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T01:04:53.000Z","msg":"做實事嘅能力零"},{"pid":"c76ad979d483034afcbef7640e11